The paper discusses cloud security engineering efforts and proposes a new approach to defending against potential intruders. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the use of virtual machines and cloud service infrastructures, which are related to distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper presents evaluations of the proposed approach, which involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
